title: Adobe Photoshop CC 2014 (64 bit) (Crack)
description:
FOLOW THIS STEPS CAREFULLY FOR A CLEAN INSTALL!


1. Close your internet connection. IMPORTANT

2. Install application from "Adobe CC 2014" folder by double
     clicking on the "Set-up.exe" (With admin rights on your system.)

3. Choose TRY install. 

   * Check the pictures in "Install pictures" folder.

4. Select your language. (You can not change it after installation)

5. Open the application as trial and select "Continue trial" and close.

  ** IMPORTANT : If you miss this step you will not have 3D option

   *** Application may close suddenly - do not worry and continue.

6. Copy "amtlib.dll" from "crack" folder and paste it in to installation
     folder by overwriting (replacing). It is generally ;

  C:Program FilesAdobeAdobe Photoshop CC 2014 
   - OR -
  C:Program Files (x86)AdobeAdobe Photoshop CC 2014

7. IMPORTANT, use your firewall to stop internet connection of 
     application and uncheck automatic updates. Don't update it.

Enjoy!
